License: UNKNOWN
Description: # ptcime
        Small time tracker built on python.
        
        ## Installation
        
        ```bash
        pip install ptcime
        ```
        
        ## Usage
        
        
        Start tracking time:
        ```bash
        ptcime start
        ```
        Stop tracking time and log currently worked on:
        ```bash    
        ptcime stop
        ```
        
        Log currently worked time:
        ```bash
        ptcime current
        ```
        
        Log day work time:
        ```bash
        ptcime day
        ```
        Log week work time:
        ```bash
        ptcime week
        ```
        
